wns the Logo Design and the Buyer has no claim on any ownership or copyrights to the Logo Design.\r\n </div><div><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">8. User Conduct and Protection</span>\r\n </b></div><div>Owrners empowers people from all corners of the globe to create, offer, purchase and sell almost any service required by society at an unbeatable price.\r\n </div><div>Owrners is friendly, community spirited and professional. Users should adhere to that while engaging in any activity or extension of the Owrners. This section concerns the expected behavior from users in as much as they are engaging each other on Owrners.\r\n </div><div>If you believe that there is a violation of our Terms or if you would like to report User Misconduct or if you have any questions concerning your account you may contact our Customer Support here.\r\n </div><div><b>8.1 Basics\r\n </b></div><div>·         Included but not limited to the following; It is prohibited to ask or offer an email address, third party messaging application, phone number or any other personal contact information with the purpose of communicating through means outside of Owrners and in a way that will bypass or exploit the Owrners messaging system or Owrners app.\r\n </div><div>·         Any information that might be needed to carry on a service that was previously conducted may be exchanged on the Order Page if needed.\r\n </div><div>·         Owrners also does not give any warranty for the quality of the service that Sellers can provide to the Buyers. You may use the dispute tools which are provided in the Order Page.\r\n </div><div>·         Owrners does not offer protection to the users who engage in other interactions other than those within the Site.\r\n </div><div>·         The information exchange, and all the files, must be done only through the Site.\r\n </div><div>·         Profanity, vulgarities, and any other language deemed by ACF as unfitting for a professional environment as well as any messages 